<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$filestorm" href="/people/filestorm">Filestorm</a>，<strong title="Artificial artificial intelligence" class="zu-question-my-bio">Artificial artificial intelligence</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="15">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhuo-xiu-47" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhuo-xiu-47" class="zg-link" title="濯锈">濯锈</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$an-qi-shi-xue-ba" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/an-qi-shi-xue-ba" class="zg-link" title="安琦是学霸">安琦是学霸</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="273097" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">几乎每种神经疾病，男女的患病几率都不相同。<br>男女大脑在解剖上的区别主要是各个区域的体积不同。我没听说过某个组织（哪怕很小的组织）是某个性别独有的。至于@曾举臣 所说的区域，我严重怀疑是Broca's area——这里主要负责语言和一方面的逻辑思考，然而从统计上说，女性比男性大。<br><br>另外就是MRI上也存在一些不同（比如情感方面）<br><br><br>细节我就不多列了。有本书专门讲这个事儿：<br>Sex Differences in the Human Brain, Their Underpinnings and Implications
<a href="/question/20232281/answer/14423556" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
